<h2 class="textheader">Welcome To Infinity Pool</h2>
<div class="textblock">
<p>Infinity Pool is a web based army builder app for the table top game infinity. It is currently in beta right now but free to use. </p>


<h3>Example List</h3>
<p>Infinity pool makes it easy to link a list to your friends <%=link_to "Yu Jing Example","/users/1/army_lists/2"%></p>
</div>
</div>
